{"type": "article", "id": 23718, "title": "在你的灯里养一些植物，看起来其实没那么怪", "description": "据设计师的说法，植物可以在灯光下成长数年。", "date": "2016-03-14T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4216, "name": "植物"}, {"id": 8906, "name": "盆栽"}, {"id": 24799, "name": "灯泡"}, {"id": 24131, "name": "多肉"}, {"id": 24832, "name": "家养"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 151, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702111224pCExJDBg7Uy0cndL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">在介绍“植物灯”之前，先来认识一对德国情侣吧。他们是 Emilia Lucht 和 Arne Sebrantke ，都是产品设计师。他们共同创建的工作室叫作 <a href=\"http://www.we-love-eames.com\">We Love Eames</a>，平时会设计一些椅子什么的。最近，他们二人共同合作设计了一款“植物灯”。LED 灯代替了日光，无需人去浇水，这是一个完全迷你的自循环系统，据两人的说法，植物可以在灯光下成长数年。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111216NUusPOjEdY8VMDwR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">植物灯</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111216S6tox97JcWBbHIyD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"> Emilia Lucht 和 Arne Sebrantke </figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111217oOSA1ypEJfv45hIi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">他们发布在官方网站上的照片</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111218J7cygoDifvlCVWu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">二人共同设计的椅子</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021112184BivJY8ULtgXedVI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">椅子作品</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111219SiY8XOm5t7dGRrZ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7825\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">在设计初期，他们设想了多种形态，最终定下了两种——吊挂式和平摆式</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111219yRbcoPeLIqnhg6BF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">制作模型</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111220ke49OYuHczfVT6xF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111220ukzYfs6awE78K0W9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">烧玻璃</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111221wPKe8sHD0Myh34t1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">快成形了</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111221dDW1eIhJyiEnTBpK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111222ujMH1deC9ql0BX3Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>如果是普通玻璃，植物在这种状态下是没法存活的。他们二人使用了一种导电的镀膜玻璃，目前正在申请专利。</p>\n<p>所谓的<a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E9%95%80%E8%86%9C%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1Y3P1uhmHPhujI-m104ryfz0ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EPj0zP1fdPjf\">镀膜玻璃</a>，就是在玻璃表面涂镀金属、合金或金属化合物薄膜，以改变玻璃的光学性能，满足某种特定的要求。导电膜玻璃早已存在，人们在玻璃表面涂敷<a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E6%B0%A7%E5%8C%96%E9%93%9F%E9%94%A1&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1Y3P1uhmHPhujI-m104ryfz0ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EPj0zP1fdPjf\">氧化铟锡</a>等<a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E5%AF%BC%E7%94%B5%E8%96%84%E8%86%9C&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1Y3P1uhmHPhujI-m104ryfz0ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EPj0zP1fdPjf\">导电薄膜</a>，通常可用于玻璃的加热、除霜、除雾，以及用作液晶显示屏等。</p>\n<p class=\"\">其实关于植物，我们曾写过不少文章呢。点击<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/18684.html\">这里</a>，可以看我们写过的空气凤梨，这是一种无须土壤、形态奇异、没有根系，维护成本很低的铁兰属植物。点击<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/23013.html\">这里</a>，你则能看到多肉植物做成的首饰，它们的设计者是美国设计师 Susan McLeary ，她的主业是设计婚礼捧花和配饰。点击<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/23203.html\">这里</a>，你则能看到全是植物的温室建筑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111222P0JrbO7XWiRBjFTn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">空气凤梨</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111223b63axe8h5juYT19y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">多肉做的首饰</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111223Odymx4qcZuXQJ2ps.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">瑞典斯德哥尔摩南部的一个办公楼概念图，它的名字是 drivhus</figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">如果你想让家里多多少少有些植物，则可以看<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/16916.html\">这篇文章</a>，它介绍了几个适合家养的新物种。</p>\n<p>题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/03/10/lamps-designed-to-grow-plants-in-windowless-spaces/\">contemporist</a></p>\n\n"}